{"tid":193322,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"《大鄉理出城》北歐三國9遊記","createTime":"2017-04-09T08:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T14:34:33.000Z","uid":53244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b25ba381a9a57d61ec1689768e238772a24c639c","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"今次係第一次分享遊記, <br />\n唔係記錄左太多detail, 只係好想分享下當中既快樂, <br />\n敬請敬巴絲們見諒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同老死2個原本打算去澳洲, <br />\n不過睇到北歐機票好平, 所以轉軚<br />\nplan左第一個星期去芬蘭, 然後去Copenhagen, 尾站先去Stockholm.<br />\n<br />\n我係上年10月入手SAS去芬蘭Helsinki既機票, <br />\n12/3 : 香港 &gt;&gt; Stockholm 轉機 &gt;&gt; Helsinki<br />\n25/3 : Stockholm &gt;&gt; 香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fyBE35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fyBE35.png&h=b8268b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寄艙行李 23kg, hand-carry唔超過7kg<br />\n來回連稅加埋hkd 3901, 好抵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n終於到左出發日, 7點前到左機場<br />\n不過大鄉理第一次去歐洲關係, 加上好怕凍<br />\n帶左好多衫, 其實真係唔洗咁多, 蠢左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為個28吋gip本身唔輕, 未出發已經 15kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79Pv7Ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79Pv7Ss.jpg&h=d28a0d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsas長途機好正, 有插頭一個同usb, 可以一路上差電,<br />\n不過我啲線入哂gip so9sad<br />\n機入面無乜影相, 總共食左3餐<br />\n2餐全餐, 1餐sandwish<br />\n同下面毒果條link個種差唔多:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/travel/art/20151001/19315877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftravel%2Fart%2F20151001%2F19315877&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2294aa29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftravel%2Fart%2F20151001%2F19315877&h=ac047d01\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/travel/art/20151001/19315877</a><br />\n<br />\n飛左11個鐘終於到左轉機站--斯德哥爾摩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8cj9jL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8cj9jL.jpg&h=fb325d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時周圍都仲係冰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一落地就要過當地immd, <br />\n我用bno順利過關, 朋友用特衰就俾鬼婆問左幾條問題先放行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實bno幫助性唔是好大, <br />\n因為當地人唔多唔少都有啲歧視亞洲人, <br />\n之後我過海關就體驗到<br />\n話說過關部機DO我, 鬼婆海關就叫我埋黎搜身,<br />\ncheck完一輪就話ok, 示意我拎袋,<br />\n拎完袋就轉身走, 點知佢攔住我大叫NO! I didn't mean you can leave<br />\n我反問: ok, so what is next?<br />\n佢就話: nothing, you can now leave<br />\n然後同後面班同鄉用土話blablabla再大笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(離境個日都有差唔多情況, 之後再講)<br />\n<br />\n最後都成功轉機到逹芬蘭首都 -- 赫爾辛基<br />\n去到係香港時間晚上11點幾, 當地下午4點左右,<br />\n一到埗就搵巴士去酒店,<br />\n由於我地第二日朝早會坐內陸機上北部 Rovaniemi,<br />\n所以揀左機場附近既酒店過一晚,<br />\n而機場都有免費shuttle bus俾旅客去機場附近既酒店.<br />\n下圖係巴士站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4teiso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4teiso.jpg&h=bfc3de1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時氣溫只有2度, 啲風打埋黎都幾醒神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等左半粒鐘架車終於到,<br />\n因為我地去到個陣已經係冬末, <br />\n開始溶雪, 所以好多車車身都勁污糟.<br />\n<br />\n我地2個第一晚住Cumulus Resort Airport Congress Center<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qk11bnV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqk11bnV.png&h=02eb1185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Cap自 <a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=084a4b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hotels.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n都幾乾淨舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94fSg2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94fSg2i.jpg&h=4d95b695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放低哂行李就落左酒店餐廳食晚餐<br />\n叫左個鹿肉扒配薯菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iqmw9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iqmw9t.jpg&h=0cd285d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好鬼酥仲有啲血水標出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲薯波波好香好入味!<br />\n食完黎多個心太軟配雲呢拿雪糕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWq8CC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWq8CC1.jpg&h=11913d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一餐北歐菜咁就食左 &euro;60, 好撚癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n北歐之旅 Day 1, 完 ."},{"pid":"b0b9f8a451c61b37582eff1a5a49820cbc4ee883","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"補充返少少<br />\nSAS來回2程每人都有支礦泉水,<br />\n全機都有wifi, 不過經濟艙要俾120蚊港紙先有得用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n北歐人都好興每人一個細gip拎上機,<br />\n所以好快霸哂啲行李位, 因此可以的話最好早啲登機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b1e10cfd0cc9025378c59d9a98c0193a14a5e1","tid":193322,"uid":15512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"反而覺得stockholm歧視嚴重d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係條街行行下都會比人特登大力撞<br />\n係餐廳食野都比人無禮對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5e21c2db56925549a6ba37c010dfe04cdb15c6","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而覺得stockholm歧視嚴重d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係條街行行下都會比人特登大力撞<br />\n係餐廳食野都比人無禮對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩我又無俾人撞<br />\n但機場地勤&gt;海關啲人寧舍西口西面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34672f386330edaa23fd32ab7e3b8f6cd70f940c","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:12:00.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n食完酒店bufflet 早餐, 就去左附近一個名為JUMBO既大商場度kill time<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78vtrP1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78vtrP1.jpg&h=8ada26bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(cap自: <a href=\"http://www.unibail-rodamco.com/W/cms_sites/SITE_16406/images16406/group2/Nordic/Jumbo/jumbo1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.unibail-rodamco.com%2FW%2Fcms_sites%2FSITE_16406%2Fimages16406%2Fgroup2%2FNordic%2FJumbo%2Fjumbo1.jpg&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ec1d486e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.unibail-rodamco.com/W/cms_sites/SITE_16406/images16406/group2/Nordic/Jumbo/jumbo1.jpg</a>)</span><br />\n<br />\n我地主要睇超市, 想睇下有乜平手信同乾糧買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落到地下全層都俾2間大型超市佔據左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6v4uEJ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6v4uEJ7.jpg&h=38c6f450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每間出面都有個街機corner俾人打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bia7898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbia7898.jpg&h=ac53ad9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面好大好好行, 同其他西方國家個啲大同小異, 唔特別講.<br />\n<br />\n返去check out就坐返shuttle bus去機場, 出發去聖誔老人村 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n內陸機揀左挪威品牌 Norwegian<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q33m1oE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ33m1oE.jpg&h=c8684be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來回包20kg行李要hkd 1150.90, 都唔係話特別平,<br />\n不過得佢個時間最fit同平過finnair所以揀左佢.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q33m1oE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ33m1oE.jpg&h=c8684be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐左個零鐘終於到左北邊既 Rovaniemi <br />\n個行李輸送帶好靚好cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sW4SX4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsW4SX4G.jpg&h=bb7c39a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(cap自: <a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C0I2AGiXAAAvLDM.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC0I2AGiXAAAvLDM.jpg&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3a8e3739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C0I2AGiXAAAvLDM.jpg</a></span><br />\n<br />\nSanta Claus Villege既員工已經一早等緊我地. <br />\n入村前講多少少先.<br />\n我地一早買左聖誕村既冬季度假package :<br />\n價錢hkd 6715 per person, <br />\n包早午晚3餐, 4晚住宿, 機場接送, 同埋免費借雪褸雪靴:<br />\n第一日會介紹村內設施同送張cert俾你;<br />\n第二日包坐雪橇車 5km , 鹿車 3km, 同聖誔老人本尊親自黎你間cabin;<br />\n第三日朝早去動物園, 夜晚包車去睇北極光;<br />\n第四日自由活動;<br />\n第五日check out.<br />\n<br />\n職員係機場接載我地同另外一對泰國夫婦後就開車,<br />\n車程 5分鐘就到村, 直送到我地既cabin.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4G4W7i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4G4W7i.jpg&h=791afbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真。係。好。撚。靚。啊!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n房間入面有個廚房, 一張king size雙人床<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P65R4j4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP65R4j4.jpg&h=d0a31cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最正係有私人桑拿房!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1X3wS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1X3wS0.jpg&h=cc84c941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攤左無耐就出返Reception聽返每日行程同會俾基本資料你<br />\n個reception都好靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8nkJA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8nkJA9.jpg&h=89b1c962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面大概係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1cpnSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1cpnSZ.jpg&h=e7f5feda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">cap自: <a href=\"https://www.finlandtours.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/christmas-house-santa-claus-village-rovaniemi-4.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finlandtours.fi%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fchristmas-house-santa-claus-village-rovaniemi-4.jpg&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=aa468223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.finlandtours.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/christmas-house-santa-claus-village-rovaniemi-4.jpg</a></span><br />\n<br />\n個叔叔好nice, 好有耐性同帶點幽默講解行程細節, <br />\n不過芬蘭除左城市人, 其他當地人既英文都有好勁鄉音,<br />\n所以我地都聽得幾辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nreception 隔離就係手信區, <br />\n後面直通餐廳.<br />\n<br />\n之後佢地派左個職員帶住我地同頭先對泰國夫婦一齊睇下條村.<br />\n仲帶左我地黎Santa Office前影相,<br />\n話過左呢排燈就正式進入北極圈啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zzi2ET3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzi2ET3.jpg&h=b9bb9338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住會帶埋我地去個倉度試雪褸雪靴, <br />\n然後俾我地拎返去cabin, 到check out 個日放係屋內就ok<br />\n最後就送左張cert俾我地證明到過北極圈 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5Q703q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5Q703q.jpg&h=30b74209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(呢張野另外買都唔平, 都要百五港紙一張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n放低左啲褸之後我地去左食晚餐<br />\n餐廳大概係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fj9278y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFj9278y.jpg&h=8d363b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">cap自Expedia</span><br />\n<br />\n認真, 成個package好抵, 唯獨個餐真係好難食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbufflet選擇少, 個湯好杰好難飲, 算劣食.<br />\n自己另外俾錢就好好多, 不過我地都想慳得就慳, <br />\n所以為求飽肚算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完一出返外面就落雪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大個人第一次見到雪咋, 個下好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後再去Santa Office影埋個靚夜景就返房焗桑拿啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9BN5nV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9BN5nV.jpg&h=3aa1e514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2MG0bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2MG0bb.jpg&h=d3d4b3cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a1cba12056d01c250b940326afd2055b4408045","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"又補充少少<br />\n<br />\n聖誕老人村每年都有唔同package揀,<br />\n啱啱上網睇左黎緊冬季package<br />\nday 4行程多左Snowmoblie<br />\n但貴左好多, 平均一位Hkd 10,710 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c480bced238844885c97490a586e46ce8c9e91b","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"推下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8102c9b415253d7274c81d1cab6c2fd823ad137","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"打緊day 3<br />\n今晚/聽朝出, <br />\n歡迎提問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b562f4439b599f431d2cefdc1f527848c65d5b6","tid":193322,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"過關一定長期拎住本bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係比d歐洲佬當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d02d716a7dd30379d759fd2b8162516ae1bff2","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過關一定長期拎住本bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係比d歐洲佬當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋排歐盟通道快好多<br />\n雖然好快脫歐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8510aacd8d369bfb52dcc1901348fc75abcf1a","tid":193322,"uid":39793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:25:24.000Z","msg":"試過係Stockholm 麥當勞 野都未食完俾人趕 但明明側邊啲local 食完唔走都冇人趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58725c5270b866bcea8da0b0aba255089ff29104","tid":193322,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"頭已側<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f21daa065d78b6323491ff8fc1f246424e34b19","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭已側<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry 絲打 <br />\n有無辦法搞下啲相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我 rotate完再up都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1735ad111316f04296824c4ceabc766ea8c95a","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"Day 3 一早去Huskey farm坐狗車<br />\n大概有10隻狗一架車, <br />\n每一round都會換狗, 以免太熱同太攰<br />\n候選既狗狗會係籠到吠, 係咁引人去摸佢地同揀佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3Oy6xv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3Oy6xv.jpg&h=e39e63ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一架車最多坐2個人, 職員會幫我地冚張真鹿皮保暖,<br />\n然後就開車!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hoo521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hoo521.jpg&h=eda41508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n架車都好快, 啲風打埋黎都好凍下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個陣 -5度, 但對啲狗黎講仍然太熱,<br />\n所以有狗狗一路跑一路食雪降溫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完會邀請我地入蒙古包飲杯熱苺汁.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zh4Z6f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzh4Z6f1.jpg&h=b7db055c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地一路飲一路同個職員姨姨傾計.<br />\n佢話全球暖化問題好嚴重, <br />\n幾年前同月份都有 -15度, <br />\n先係狗同鹿最舒服既溫度, <br />\n而我地平時見既huskey唔會跑, <br />\n因為個種純種狗既毛更厚更密, <br />\n無-15度都唔會俾佢地跑, 一定中硬暑.<br />\n<br />\n玩完狗車就去左食lunch bufflet,<br />\n下午再去馴鹿場玩鹿車.<br />\n呢個真係早去有著數.<br />\n因為佢會一出就出2架車, 一前一後,<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm23Qeq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm23Qeq.jpg&h=4d7b5a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早黎佢會安排坐前個架車, 成個view都無遮掩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9e5FSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9e5FSw.jpg&h=660460b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鹿車相比狗車雖然好慢, <br />\n但睇既境好正, 好仙境feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐前面架車有另一個advantage,<br />\n就係後面車隻鹿有機會行到好近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZR0258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZR0258.jpg&h=cbc882b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐完車仲會請食bbq大腸同飲苺汁取暖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrHf2T3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrHf2T3.jpg&h=72c509f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完一日車就返cabin等聖誕老人黎探訪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一黎就敲窗唔係敲門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSanta好高, 有2米3, 成個海格咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oqs0DHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqs0DHT.jpg&h=7d38b13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢知我地係香港人就用廣東話講&quot;恭喜發財&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要我地唱歌跳舞先肯派小禮物俾我地<br />\n禮物係茶包一盒同聖誕村吊飾一個 (呢個野都要&euro;6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4J32nK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4J32nK4.jpg&h=e1c96a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁完左DAY 3啦"},{"pid":"b17d7c26d12dc815e971fe04db2fb77a1fff4d66","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a0e80993a9db6c5ea21370d6c61f6b27f81aa3","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過係Stockholm 麥當勞 野都未食完俾人趕 但明明側邊啲local 食完唔走都冇人趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nStockholm留左3日半唔多<br />\n慶幸無遇到咁差<br />\n不過係max burger係多白人望住哂"},{"pid":"5f7aacd0aac871946205d7661a9552505bb62c29","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"聽日再update <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16749d6ac782106d6d606992a624a3f2455f4ae4","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"香港好潮濕<br />\n好掛住芬蘭啲天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b09d023fe5e3c29d7fc4f8956c00250386015db","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"Day 4仍然係Santa Village<br />\n今日由靚女職員揸車載去Ranua Zoo.<br />\n係集合左最多北極圈動物既動物園<br />\n入面有好多鷹、貓頭鷹、北極狐、北極熊等動物睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iq7yur39\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiq7yur39&h=aca34576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/97xlbdfe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F97xlbdfe&h=7417af4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xs5wa3eg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxs5wa3eg&h=3746971a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地仲好好彩撞啱當地首隻北極熊BB第一次見人既日子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/naq9xg8s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnaq9xg8s&h=979612dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(不過好遠好難影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢隻係經手熊 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z6u9f58e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz6u9f58e&h=8c482f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面仲有間Ice Bar<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gmzo15ta\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgmzo15ta&h=103d1b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今次午餐會係園區食, <br />\n會有芬蘭道地既三文魚忌廉湯飲 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/63cpbuqg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F63cpbuqg&h=5bc65118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(Cap自TripAdvisor)</span><br />\n<br />\n返到村就同朋友去左手信街影多次北極圈線<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m2u4orn0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm2u4orn0&h=552ef19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少得梗係去寄呢度獨有既Postcard啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qj6mtoge\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqj6mtoge&h=dd25f295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度係最多遊客既地方。<br />\n啲postcard大概1星期左右就寄到香港啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/scn8obd5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fscn8obd5&h=f8fad0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚就有重頭戲---極光之旅!!!<br />\n本身都好擔心睇唔到<br />\n因為抵埗個日到今朝都落雪,<br />\n啲雲好厚, KP得1<br />\n好好彩臨出發前2個鐘個天就露曙光, 雲開始散!<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hj2s5b6a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhj2s5b6a&h=e8b066f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地晚上9點係Reception集合, <br />\n一共2車人去附近一個湖上追光<br />\n出發前司機話今晚kp 3, 睇到光既機會都好大, 不過去到仍要等, Mothernature既野好難估。<br />\n坐大概20分鐘車程就到<br />\n然後奇蹟就出現....<br />\n一落車就見到一道淡黃淡綠色既極光帶出現啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dlecxvim\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdlecxvim&h=c8322a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係等都唔洗等! 個個拿拿聲衝落車set腳架影光!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/prbym6wj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fprbym6wj&h=1ed9c414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fa6xicty\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffa6xicty&h=da17df65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hedn5yj0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhedn5yj0&h=180e992f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽，我得左啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個下真心有流眼淚, 因為完左一項bucket list, 而且我地真係非常好彩, 係太陽風暴水尾仲見到真係好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個晚返到村11點幾連村內都見到極光!!<br />\n不過太多燈光就睇得相對無咁清楚"},{"pid":"2b2aeba0b4b55bcb8295a1d7e0bca4dd657920b8","tid":193322,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"大鄉里個post名改得衰無人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648752cc941157d2589dd031fdd3085e236d63fa","tid":193322,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82d3ed7dec2f6f39f4da371a49ef26692b2c549","tid":193322,"uid":61436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大鄉里個post名改得衰無人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能少人去/想去"}]}